ponsive.</li>\n<li>Adding light_rounded Pretty Photo theme.</li>\n<li>Twitter widget is removed. Reason for this is that Twitter has discontinued its unauthenticated v1.0 API! Twitter wants your only option for on-page widgets to be their own Embedded Timelines that you can use in the default Text widget.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 2.1.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Improving language translation.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 2.1.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixing product variation problem.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 2.1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Implementing WooShop notifier</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 2.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updating CSS to work with the Woocommerce 2.0.12</li>\n<li>Fixing Email Order Items bug .</li>\n<li>Adding Login/Logout to the top menu .</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updating number of items in cart in the upper right corner so that it works in the Woocommerce 2.0 .</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Adding dynamic link to the View Cart page on the upper right shopping cart icon.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update engine changes.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial theme version.</li>\n</ul>\n]]>\n	</changelog>\n</notifier>','yes'),(1237,'notifier-cache-last-updated-wooshoplite-2-2-3','1420962510','yes'),(1238,'optionsframework','a:2:{s:2:\"id\";s:12:\"woovardhaman\";s:12:\"knownoptions\";a:2:{i:0;s:11:\"wooshoplite\";i:1;s:12:\"woovardhaman\";}}','yes'),(1240,'wooshoplite','a:25:{s:23:\"dessky_sidebar_position\";s:4:\"left\";s:16:\"dessky_logo_type\";s:9:\"imagelogo\";s:16:\"dessky_site_name\";s:0:\"\";s:14:\"dessky_tagline\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"dessky_logo_image\";s:78:\"http://10.40.21.74/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Shop_Logo1-300x51.png\";s:14:\"dessky_favicon\";s:68:\"http://10.40.21.74/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/favicon.ico\";s:13:\"dessky_footer\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"dessky_google\";s:0:\"\";s:22:\"dessky_body_background\";a:5:{s:5:\"color\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"image\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"repeat\";s:6:\"repeat\";s:8:\"